# Community Guidelines

## Be Respectful
Respect all members of the community. Discussions and contributions should be conducted with professionalism and politeness.

## Collaboration
We encourage collaboration. Please be open to feedback and ready to give constructive feedback to others.

## Stay on Topic
Keep discussions relevant to the project and its goals.

## Help Each Other
If you see someone struggling or with a question, feel free to help them out. Our community thrives on mutual support.

## Enforcement
Violations of these guidelines will be addressed on a case-by-case basis. Repeat or severe violations may result in temporary or permanent bans from the community.

